## Quality thresholds

| Metric | PASS | WARN | FAIL |
|--------|------|------|------|
| Mean per-base Q | ≥ 28 | 20–28 | < 20 |
| Reads with Q < 20 | < 10% | 10–30% | > 30% |
| N-base content | < 1% | 1–5% | > 5% |
| GC content | 40–60% | outside range | — |

